content: I’d like to go to Walz’ Reno rally tomorrow.  Where do I register? Where is it? What time?
It will likely be invite only, and those who RSVPed and are confirmed will not receive final location or timing details until the night before or morning of. For security reasons.
If there is a public link to RSVP for this one, maybe someone can point you in the right direction on here but you can always check events.democrats.org
I know the text team was sending invites. Perhaps ask in there and see if the invite link still has availability. <#1266829704204386334>
Thank you, Kay Adams & Holly Mate- Luber!
FYI, I think I saw somewhere this morning that the rally has been postponed due to the fire nearby
